ell und verständlich mit Beispielsfällen und Schaubildern informieren und Lösungsansätze entwickeln.  aThis second, completely revised edition engages with current case law (with an emphasis on German law) to answer legal questions faced by librarians and all information institution employees in their day-to-day work. New chapters on provenance research and data protection have been added. Case studies and graphics are included to help non-lawyers develop problem-solving approaches, as well as provide up-to-date and understandable information.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aCopyrightxElectronic information resourceszGermany. 0aCopyrightzGermany. 0aFair use (Copyright)zGermany. 0aInformation serviceszGermany. 0aLegal researchzGermanyvHandbooks, manuals, etc. 0aLibrariansxLegal status, laws, etczGermany. 0aLibrarieszGermany. 0aLibrary administrationzGermanyvHandbooks, manuals, etc. 0aLibrary legislationzGermanyvHandbooks, manuals, etc. 4aBibliothekar/Recht. 4aRecht/Bibliothek. 4aUrheberrecht. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Library & Information Science / General.2bisacsh  aLaw/Library.  aLibrarian/Law.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Library and Information Science 2020z9783110704686oZDB-23-DGB0 cEPUBz97831106360860 cprintz978311063567640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311064038040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110640380423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110640380/original  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1b2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LB  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_E